I'm quite accustomed to people persecuting us.

00:18:03.501 --> 00:18:05.301
It's been going on for thousands of years.

00:18:05.302 --> 00:18:09.502
Native Americans, they studied crystals, the ancient Chinese, Belgians,

00:18:09.503 --> 00:18:12.503
Superman, they all studied crystals.

