00:18:31.510 --> 00:18:35.510
And there, under the magnolia tree, a woman breastfeeding a baby elk.

00:18:35.511 --> 00:18:37.511
Do you see it? It's nature.

00:18:37.512 --> 00:18:38.812
Ew, gross.

00:18:38.813 --> 00:18:42.013
You're one of those filthy hippies that thinks breastfeeding in public is okay?

00:18:42.014 --> 00:18:43.514
Well, it's not.

00:18:43.515 --> 00:18:46.515
There are bottles and milk at the store. Don't act like a cow.

00:18:46.516 --> 00:18:50.016
You really remind me of someone, by the way.

00:18:50.017 --> 00:18:53.017
See, Amy, you're putting the blinders of society on.

00:18:53.018 --> 00:18:56.518
We're all the same. I remind you of yourself, of every man and woman.

00:18:56.519 --> 00:18:58.519
Mm, mm-mm. No, not of them.

