The knife ceremony is very important and spiritual.

00:26:41.094 --> 00:26:43.414
It's an ancient one-person personal crisis.

00:27:00.000 --> 00:27:03.810
you say to yourself, I'm going to have a spiritual experience,

00:27:03.811 --> 00:27:05.811
or thrust this thing into my head.

