Life actors never rehearse and need no script, Amy.

00:27:09.811 --> 00:27:12.211
That was said by somebody really spaced out.

00:27:12.212 --> 00:27:16.212
And I'm going to say it again, like the wind which keeps blowing, or the sun which shines with life.

00:27:16.213 --> 00:27:17.613
Will you please leave?

00:27:17.614 --> 00:27:21.214
You smell and you talk really weird and you're just really gross.

00:27:21.215 --> 00:27:24.815
Not until I tell people out there, become an internationalist.

00:27:24.816 --> 00:27:28.216
Learn oral traditions, learn to respect life.

00:27:28.217 --> 00:27:32.217
Make war on machines, marry your mother.

