Knights of the road, here's your stallion.

00:56:16.000 --> 00:56:17.517
The car for freedom.

00:56:17.518 --> 00:56:18.518
Freedom.

00:56:18.519 --> 00:56:20.519
The car for hot excitement.

00:56:20.520 --> 00:56:21.520
Excitement.

00:56:21.521 --> 00:56:24.821
The car for a man who is alone against the elements.

00:56:25.317 --> 00:56:26.817
The Mybatsu Thunder.

00:56:27.517 --> 00:56:29.817
The pride is back.

00:56:29.818 --> 00:56:31.518
It's the power of a compact.

00:56:31.519 --> 00:56:33.519
Looks small, but it's so big.

00:56:33.520 --> 00:56:34.820
Fuel injected.

00:56:34.821 --> 00:56:35.821
Inject me.

00:56:35.822 --> 00:56:39.522
Mybatsu Thunder. On the toll road of life, you have to pay to prove you can.

00:56:39.523 --> 00:56:41.523
Live the emotion of an individual.

00:56:41.524 --> 00:56:42.524
Thunder.

00:56:42.525 --> 00:56:45.525
The awesome power of nature distilled into one vehicle.

00:56:45.526 --> 00:56:48.026
Because after you get struck by lightning,

00:56:50.517 --> 00:56:51.817
there's thunder.

00:56:52.017 --> 00:56:53.817
The Mybatsu Thunder.

00:57:00.000 --> 00:57:03.510
What's this I found under your bed?

00:57:03.511 --> 00:57:06.591
The only angles you're going to read is Laura Engel's Wilder.

00:57:07.510 --> 00:57:10.010
If you think your child might be a red,

00:57:10.011 --> 00:57:11.611
here are some warning signs.

00:57:11.612 --> 00:57:14.792
They read complicated literature and have concern for their fellow man.

00:57:14.793 --> 00:57:16.313
They even like to share.

00:57:16.314 --> 00:57:24.994
Tell your kids if someone approaches them with pamphlets about recycling, an invitation to a labor rally, or showing any doubts about the fairness of our system, then they should find a teacher or a policeman immediately.

00:57:27.590 --> 00:57:29.670
Do yourself a favor.

00:57:30.030 --> 00:57:32.470
Take both hands off the wheel and touch the stereo.

00:57:32.870 --> 00:57:34.390
Do you feel the power?

00:57:34.830 --> 00:57:42.030
Ah, yes, friend, there's a lot of evil in the world, but there is also light. And I have been sent to shine a light on all degenerates, philanderers, liberals, and other evil doers,

00:57:42.031 --> 00:57:44.311
and expose them for what they really are.

00:57:44.312 --> 00:57:46.912
Don't waste your money on unnecessary and

00:57:48.230 --> 00:57:49.990
give it to me.

00:57:50.510 --> 00:57:52.430
There's only one thing that will save you.

00:57:52.431 --> 00:57:57.431
A highly fortified structure in the shape of the most powerful thing on the planet,

00:57:57.432 --> 00:57:58.432
me.

00:57:58.830 --> 00:58:03.830
Degenerates will ruin this great city. In my wonderful book, I tell of the impending disaster about to befall this planet.

00:58:03.831 --> 00:58:08.431
Nuclear holocaust, plagues of flying rodents, the seas rising up and turning yellow.

00:58:08.432 --> 00:58:12.032
It is coming. It is written by me, but you can save yourself.

