The first course I call think, hold that thought, complete, because that's what you do.

01:13:19.032 --> 01:13:23.032
Step two is known as learn, start doing, where I explain the mysteries of starting.

01:13:23.033 --> 01:13:24.513
Or take the new accelerator

01:13:30.000 --> 01:13:32.500
of course that will have you laughing at hugging strangers.

01:13:32.501 --> 01:13:35.001
Motivate, demonstrate, then motivate again.

01:13:35.002 --> 01:13:38.802
Just listen to these endorsements and remember, these people volunteered, they aren't being paid much.

01:13:39.600 --> 01:13:44.900
I've been on the think hold that thought complete program and I have to say, I'm finally going to start my career in being a well-paid rich person.

01:13:45.200 --> 01:13:48.000
Yeah, I've been thinking my way to success for a while now.

01:13:48.001 --> 01:13:49.501
It's some good stuff.

01:13:49.800 --> 01:13:52.200
Call now and sign up for my think your way to success program.

